  <rte>
    <name>Helvellyn and Raise from Swirls</name>
    <desc>Helvellyn, England's third highest mountain, is a popular mountain. This Lake District walk ascends from Thirlmere and then heads north along the ridge to use a less frequented route for the descent.</desc>
